name: GINGER GANG
description: Ginger Gang lands to kickass in the name of gains & freedom. A crazy memecoin uniting the crypto world around the first crypto-friendly US administration. With our Ginger Gang - badass renegades here to protect President Trump, reboot crypto, & fly us all to the moon. Protecting innovation, crushing hacks, & securing prosperity - for the memecoin market & beyond. Let's go beyond the space and make names.
